plot: Nombre Original: a cross the universeDirector: romain gavrasActores: gaspard auge, Xavier de RosnayA Cross the Universe is a live album and documentary film by Justice, released in 2008. Its title is a reference to the John Lennon-penned Beatles song "Across the Universe" released in 1969, and the band's own album †.
